data.description: Lowest priced home over 2,600 SQFT in Golden Gates Estates! NO HOA! 2.5 acres of completely fenced and gated land with nearly 3,000 SQFT of living space. Renovated cabinets with a center island, new KitchenAid appliances, and quartz countertops greet you in the kitchen, as well as a walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom features a tray ceiling with hardwood floors, two walk-in closets, and French doors leading you out to the pool. Open floor plan with split bedrooms as well as two living areas, two dining rooms, and a whole house security system to protect it all. All bedrooms include new hardwood flooring as well as high ceilings throughout the home. The roof was replaced in 2018 and a deep well pump was installed in 2023. On the exterior, you will find a 3-car garage as well as 2 entry points into the open-spaced attic, and huge outdoor living in the back with a relaxing pool. Only 10 minutes to Publix, dining, shopping, and 15 minutes to the Big Corkscrew Island Regional Park!
